info.longDescription:
Dentists  in Albania at Biodent Dental Clinic  are pioneers in the field of  dental tourism , boasting more than 15 years of experience with patients coming not only from Europe, but also from America.

We also have several active collaborations with  dental clinics  throughout the country. A calm and friendly environment, composed of the best professionals in the sector who will take care of the patient from his  arrival in Tirana .

We use state-of-the-art machinery, we meticulously choose our products and we guarantee every service provided through appropriate certification, such as the  implant passport .
